Map Title          : Pool (with HDR)
Map Version        : v1.0 Final
Author             : dark_webber
Website            : NA

============================

Game               : Counter Strike Source
Supported Gametype : Gun Game
Map Size           : 18 players (9vs9)

============================

Contents of this Package : This is a custom map made for CSS, wich takes place at a pool house.

============================

Installation Instructions : Copy pool.bsp to the folder C:\Program Files\Valve\SteamApps\[username]\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps where Valve is you installation directory and username is your Steam account username.
